Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and there'd be no one there to say it.\NThe ego will create a feeling of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,oblivion and you go into oblivion\Nbecause oblivion is not the same as the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,ultimate reality. You can't stay there\Nand you come out of oblivion and you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,find yourself three years old in a\Nlittle cart. [laughter]
